The Infinite Maze: Project License
Alexander Cripple · 2026

1. Integrity Clause
Core Preservation: While remixes, adaptations, and translations are permitted, the "Three Pillars" of the project—Morphystic Social Design, Wittgenstein-Greek-Germanic Austerity, and the Infinite Game—must remain the foundation of any derivative work.

Doctrine Alignment: Any game built from this document must respect the core principles of the Morphysm Doctrine.

2. Non-Commercial Restriction
No Sale: This is a cultural and artistic project.

Prohibition: Selling this Game Design Document, the resulting software, or any derivative works for money is strictly prohibited.

3. Attribution & Sharing
Credit: Any use of these ideas or files must attribute Alexander Cripple as the original designer.

ShareAlike: If you remix, transform, or build upon this material, you must distribute your contributions under this same license.

